<example id="example" otherprops="examples"><title>Example</title>
      <p>The following code sample shows how an image is referenced.  The <xmlatt>placement</xmlatt>
        attribute is set to "break"; this ensures that the image is not rendered inline.</p><codeblock>&lt;image href="bike.gif" placement="break"&gt;
